Freeture
--------

Fripon version: `git clone https://github.com/fripon/freeture.git`

DFN version: `git clone https://github.com/hdevillepoix/freeture.git`

Classic GNU build, except might need `./configure ARV_CFLAGS='-I/usr/local/include/aravis-0.6/' ARV_LIBS='-L/usr/local/lib/ -laravis-0.5 -lm`



